## Project Context

- **Client:** Chick-fil-A College Football Hall of Fame (cfbhall.com)
- **Agency work:** Client-shareable **search prototype** for presentation + Figma import later
- **This repo:** Static prototype ‚Äî **NOT** production Umbraco
- **CMS target (later):** Umbraco Search / Examine index ‚Äî **NO Search & Filter Pro**

---

## What We Are Building

1. Global header search ‚Äî default **icon** ‚Üí expand to input (desktop + mobile) ‚Äî **inline, Option A**
2. Predictive dropdown ‚Äî HOF (avatar + team badge) vs general (text/icon)
3. `/search` page ‚Äî query hero, **right** category filters, result cards, empty state
4. Mock Umbraco backend ‚Äî local `search-index.json` (Examine-shaped documents)

Primary user intents: **inductees**, **tickets**, **events**.

---

## Tech Stack (do not change without asking)

- Prefer **vanilla HTML / CSS / JS**
- **No** React/Next unless Matt explicitly switches
- **No** Search & Filter Pro or other paid search plugins
- Fonts: Kaneda + Neusa Next (or approved stand-ins) ‚Äî **not Inter / Roboto / Arial as brand faces**
- Brand colors live in `tokens.css` only

